Working with the Raleigh Police Incidents 'shell' file 10


After extracting the zip file, browse to the Templates folder and open Raleigh_Police_Incidents_v01.pbix  file.




The Power BI Report file is a 'shell' of the project and it will help you get started.


The 'shell' Power BI Report file, .pbix file, has the following:

  1. Overview page - an overview picture of the project.
  2. RaleighPoliceIncidents Dashboard page - it contains an image, title and trademark message
  3. RaleighPoliceIncidents-District Dashboard page - it contains an image, title and trademark message, Year over Year image
  4. RaleighPoliceIncidents-Street Dashboard page - it contains an image, title and trademark message


Click on File ->  Save and save the file to your PC/NoteBook.
